Package: pivottabler
Type: Package
Title: Create Pivot Tables natively in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Bailiss", email = "cbailiss@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: pivottabler enables regular pivot tables to be 
    created in just a few lines of R.  More complex pivot tables can 
    also be created, e.g. with irregular layouts, multiple calculations 
    and/or derived calculations based on multiple data frames. 
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    R6 (>= 2.2.0),
    dplyr (>= 0.5.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.1),
    htmltools(>= 0.3.5),
    htmlwidgets (>= 0.8)
Suggests:
    listviewer (>= 1.4.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/cbailiss/pivottabler
BugReports: https://github.com/cbailiss/pivottabler/issues
